    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">- Augmented the built-in grep (:WinGrep, :ArgGrep, :BufGrep)<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;functionality with the new command :GrepBufs to grep specified<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;buffers only. This is very similar to unix :grep command with given<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;filenames.<br>- New commands :GOpen, :GClose and :GWindow on the lines of :copen,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;:cclose and :cwindow to work with the preview window. The existing<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;commands :GNext, :GPrev and :GG commands now work globally, just like<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;the :cnext, :cprev and :cc commands.<br>- Fixed misc. bugs.<br></td>
